OL,3,CNew legislation proposed to tackle
OL,4,Cviolence against women and girls in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FJersey's Justice and Home Affairs
OL,8,FMinister has lodged "key legislation"
OL,9,Fto tackle violence against women and
OL,10,Fgirls (VAWG).
OL,12,FThe draft amendments expand
OL,13,Fdefinitions and create new offences to
OL,14,Fhold perpetrators to account, from
OL,15,Fsharing intimate images of another
OL,16,Fperson without their consent, to
OL,17,Fstalking and strangulation.
