OL,3,CNew legislation proposed to tackle
OL,4,Cviolence against women and girls in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FThe primary aim of this legislation is
OL,8,Fto improve how the criminal justice
OL,9,Fsystem can respond to intimate image
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FThis refers to the non-consensual
OL,13,Fpossession, recording and sharing of
OL,14,Fnude or sexual images.
OL,16,FThe draft law also includes
OL,17,Fcriminalising cyber-flashing,
OL,18,Fcyberstalking, and the use of deep
OL,19,Ffakes.
