OL,3,CNew legislation proposed to tackle
OL,4,Cviolence against women and girls in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FThis draft law would introduce more
OL,8,Frobust offences relating to harassment
OL,9,Fand stalking and introduce additional
OL,10,Fmeasures to strengthen the protections
OL,11,Ffor victims of stalking, regardless of
OL,12,Fconviction.
OL,14,FBetween 2016-2021, 192 reports of
OL,15,Fstalking were made to the States of
OL,16,FJersey Police.
OL,18,FHowever, only two of the reports
OL,19,Fresulted in convictions.
