OL,3,CNew legislation proposed to tackle
OL,4,Cviolence against women and girls in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FUnder new arrangements, if a police
OL,8,Fofficer believes that a person is a
OL,9,Fvictim of domestic abuse, they can be
OL,10,Fgranted legal protections immediately,
OL,11,Feven before the case goes to court.
OL,13,FIn cases where the suspect and victim
OL,14,Flive together, it could mean the
OL,15,Faccused would be forced to leave the
OL,16,Fhome and bar them from reentering.
