OL,3,CNew legislation proposed to tackle
OL,4,Cviolence against women and girls in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FThis amendment would introduce a
OL,8,Fstandalone offence of non-fatal
OL,9,Fstrangulation.
OL,11,FCurrently, it can only be prosecuted
OL,12,Funder the Domestic Abuse Law, which
OL,13,Fcan complicate legal charges.
OL,15,FIn Jersey, a total of 116 crimes
OL,16,Frelated to strangulation were recorded
OL,17,Fby the States of Jersey Police between
OL,18,F2019 and November 2025.
