OL,7,FThe Draft Crime (Public Order)
OL,8,F(Jersey) Amendment Law 202-
OL,10,FThis law would expand the definition
OL,11,Fof a criminal threat to include
OL,12,Fthreats to commit the "most serious
OL,13,Fsexual offences".
OL,15,FCurrently, the Public Order Law
OL,16,Fprovides that threats meet the
OL,17,Fcriminal threshold if they are to
OL,18,F'kill, rape or cause serious physical
OL,19,Finjury to any person'.
